{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Transferable","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Transferable","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Transferable\"><code>Transferable</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for DOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Transferable</strong></code> 接口代表一个能在不同可执行上下文之间，列如主线程和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a> 之间，相互传递的对象。</p>\n\n<p>这是一个抽象接口，没有任何对象属于此类型。它也没有定义任何方法和属性；它只是一个标签，用来指示对象在特定场合下，比如如通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\"><code>Worker.postMessage()</code></a> 方法传递到 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>，是可用的。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>备注：</strong>技术上，<code>Transferable</code> 接口已不复存在。但是，<code>Transferable</code> 对象的<em>效用</em>依旧存在，只是其实现被移到了更加底层的位置。（转而通过<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WebIDL\">WebIDL <small>(en-US)</small></a> 拓展属性 <code>[Transferable]</code> 实现）。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a> 实现了此接口。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>Transferable</code></em><em> 接口没有实现或继承任何属性。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>Transferable</code> 接口</em><em>没有实现或继承任何方法。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">评语</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#transferable-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Transferable</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>使用 Web IDL 拓展属性 <code>[Transferable]</code> 代替 <code>Transferable 接口</code>。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/infrastructure.html#transferable-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Transferable</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>初始定义。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.Transferable","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>实现了它的接口：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a>、 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Transferable 接口代表一个能在不同可执行上下文之间，列如主线程和 Worker 之间，相互传递的对象。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Transferable","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Transferable","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Transferable","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/transferable","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/transferable/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Transferable","title":"Transferable"}],"pageTitle":"Transferable - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}